sys_user_role.description: This role is assigned to users who play the role of supervisors in the Inventory Management application. Supervisors have permission to perform any operation on all tables and fields within the application. This includes creating, reading, updating, and deleting records. Supervisors are responsible for overseeing and efficiently managing processes in the application.
